<h3 id="ssti-using-ejs-custom-delimiters">SSTI using EJS custom delimiters</h3>

<p>Using the same logic, I tried passing to the template some non-string parameters, noticing that we weren’t limited to using only string values, but we were also able to pass arrays or objects to the server.</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>GET /991a04f8-fecd-42f9-af93-31d29f13420c?name[root]=/tmp&amp;name[foo]=pippo
Host: 127.0.0.1:9086


